With their contoured cheekbones, sultry smokey eyes and glossy hair, the Kardashian sisters never look less than perfect.

The secret behind their good looks? Make-up lessons! 

Kendall Jenner, one of the youngest of the clan, has revealed that Kim, Khloe and Kourtney spent their juvenile years at beauty school.

Speaking in an interview with fellow model Joan Smalls, the 19-year-old said: 'Randomly enough, my older sisters went to a make-up school when they were younger, so they’re all really good at it. They’ve always told me that “natural is better.”'

