Joan, a supermodel herself, interviewed Kendall to celebrate her joining the Estee Lauder family.

Speaking about her new role, the burgeoning star said: 'I was so excited. I found out backstage in Paris and they told me I couldn’t say anything. So I saw the text and I was like, “Oh my God! I have to keep this to myself.” 

'When I got to my room I started freaking out.  My mom was the only person I told. She was crying, but then she cries at everything.'

